https://github.com/apache/incubator-superset/pull/3993
I just have it merged. Please let me know if it works for you!

LGTM

@timifasubaa we removed all the `DangerouslySetInnerHtml` calls resently as they represent a vector of script injection. The alternative is to consider the error message as a React `node`as it gets passed around, though it may flow through Redux in which case it may be an anti-pattern to put nodes in the Redux store.

The easy & secure solution is to remove the tags.
